title: Muv-Luv Alternative Chronicles Vol.3
description: Contains The Day After episode 02, an Alternative prequel/sidestory featuring the Isumi Valkyries entitled Muv-Luv Alternative Chronicles: Saitan, a drama CD supplement to The Day After, a new episode of Total Eclipse Radio featuring Sugita Tomokazu alongside the usual personalities, a new episode of age's old web radio, a Revoltech special feature, a wallpaper collection, and a PV for the upcoming animated adaptation of Muv-Luv Alternative: Total Eclipse
